      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What types of assessments does iMocha offer?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "iMocha offers 3,000+ ready-to-use assessments covering coding, cognitive, situational judgment, and non-tech roles — along with project-based assessments and an AI-powered skills intelligence cloud. AssessIQ offers coding tests (with live execution and test-case scoring), multiple-choice, aptitude, and subjective questions with structured rubric grading."
